description: Experience unparalleled coastal living at Pier 4, Boston Seaport’s premier boutique residence. This stunning 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence features open-concept living with expansive windows, flooding the home with natural light and showcasing sweeping water views. Both en-suite bedrooms include custom closets, built-ins, and spa-like baths. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with top-tier Gaggenau appliances, a marble waterfall island. A private deck offers the perfect setting to enjoy the serene harbor vistas. All windows equipped with motorized blinds, 2 valet/self garage parkings and a private storage unit add to the convenience. Enjoy top-tier amenities including 24-hour concierge, a fitness center and a yoga studio, virtual golf, a dog spa, and an entertainment lounge with fireplace, catering kitchen, grill, and terrace overlooking the water. Fine dining awaits at Woods Hill Table and Nautilus. Enjoy local cafes, shops, habor walk, Airport&the future Commonwealth Pie.
